@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_avboik(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.cos(v1 + 0.18)) * (wp.sin(v2 + 0.39) / wp.sin(v2 + 0.74)))
    v2 = wp.sin(v1)
    v0 = wp.exp(0.80)
    v2 = v0
    v0 = wp.sin(v1)
    v2 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.92) * (v0 + 0.06 - v0 + 0.60)) * (0.92 - (v2 + 0.33 / v2 + 0.60)))
    v2 = wp.sin(0.20)
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.exp(wp.exp(v2 + 0.77)))
    data[tid] = v0
